            "id": 6124495,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 台特化(4772)大漲7.23%，報252元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台特化(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4772:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4772\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4772-TW</a>)25日10:08股價上漲17元，報252.0元，漲幅7.23%，成交3,458張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台特化(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4772:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4772\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4772-TW</a>)所屬產業為化學工業，主要業務為半導體特氣及精密化學材料之製造與買賣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌3.89%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌0.78%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-1,746 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-1,531 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+50 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-265 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,172 張</li> <li>融券增減：+10 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
